    "body" : "<p>With Java 7, you can use <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/nio/file/Files.html#createDirectories(java.nio.file.Path,%20java.nio.file.attribute.FileAttribute...)\"><code>Files.createDirectories()</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p>For instance:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Files.createDirectories(Paths.get(\"/path/to/directory\"));\n</code></pre>\n"
